    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This power unit features individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a broad powerband and a surgical throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve shim adjustment and a cooling system refresh. The suspension geometry remains precise, benefiting from refreshed bushings and dampers. While the aesthetic presentation shows light, honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical components are tuned for peak performance and longevity.",
