    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it runs like a dream and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend getaways. It\u2019s got a little bit of character from being loved, but it still looks fantastic and feels great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m just looking for a new owner who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out and come take it for a spin!",
