    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing. Power is managed through a tactile Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and delivered to the pavement via a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis has been vetted with a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural integrity under high torque loads. Suspension bushings and dampers remain firm, preserving the razor-sharp turn-in and communicative steering rack feedback characteristic of this platform. This is a mechanically robust driver\u2019s car, ready for spirited canyon runs or track-day duty.",
